  </tr>
  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>This appears to be caused by the CSRF protection. Openhatch returns a 403 error 
to the POST request, and I've confirmed that the save_profile_entry_do function 
is never called. The reason is that in the AJAX request, we don't pass in the 
CSRF token.

There's a method outlined here for how to do this: 
<a href="https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/dev/ref/contrib/csrf/">https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/dev/ref/contrib/csrf/</a></pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
  <tr>
